          "empty_state": "Connect a wearable to unlock recovery, sleep, strain, and baseline trends. Do not fabricate a readiness score.",
          "responsive_behavior": "Desktop uses gauges plus a monitor grid; mobile stacks the three headline scores then exposes monitor tiles in priority order."
        },
        {
          "id": "biomarker-context",
          "label": "Biomarker context",
          "modality": "biomarkers",
